# Fake Review Detector

An AI-powered web app that detects fake or fraudulent product reviews using NLP and Machine Learning.

## Features
- Paste any product review and get an instant verdict
- Shows Fake/Genuine score with confidence percentage
- Highlights suspicious signals (excessive caps, generic phrases, etc.)
- Clean dark UI built for presentation

## Tech Stack
- Python + Flask (Backend)
- Transformers / NLP Model (AI Detection)
- HTML + CSS + JavaScript (Frontend)

## Setup & Run

### 1. Install dependencies
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Run the app
```
python app.py
```

### 3. Open in browser
```
http://localhost:5000
```

## How it works
1. User pastes a review into the text box
2. The review is sent to the Flask backend
3. A zero-shot NLP classification model analyzes the text
4. Additional heuristic checks flag suspicious patterns
5. Result is displayed with confidence score and flags

